TDJANGOH Usage Instructions
***************************

Requirements
============

GCC > 4.4.7 with build-in GFORTRAN
ROOT > 5.34/32
LHAPDF 5.9.1
CERNLIB (2006)

(Tested on LXPLUS and CCAGE)


Compilers and Options
=====================

Put in src/Makefile the actual location of LHAPDF (path/to/LHAPDF)

To build :
  make (in the root directory of the package)


Test Program
============

Put in test/Makefile the actual location of libDjangoh (path/to/package/lib)

To build test :
  make test (in the root directory of the package)

To launch test :
  bin/test


Contact
=======

For any problem, input, questions : nicolas.pierre@cern.ch
